'''杰羅姆·邁克爾·西格爾'''（{{lang-en|Jerome Michael Segal}}；{{bd|1943年|11月25日}}）是美國[[银泉_(马里兰州)|马里兰州银泉]]的一名哲學家和政治活動家。

西格爾是[[馬里蘭大學學院市分校|馬里蘭大學學院市分校]]的研究學者和猶太和平大廳主席<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/newssearch/?datefilter=All%20Since%202005&query=jerome%20m.%20segal&sort=Relevance|title=Search - The Washington Post - Jerome M. Segal|last=|first=|date=|website=Washington Post|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181027185229/https://www.washingtonpost.com/error/not-found/|archive-date=2018-10-27|access-date=2017-12-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>，曾參與{{le|2018年馬利蘭州美國參議院議員選舉|United States Senate election in Maryland, 2018|2018年美國參議院選舉}}馬利蘭州民主黨初選<ref>{{cite news|last1=Portnoy|first1=Jenna|title=How a defiant Chelsea Manning could upend the race for U.S. Senate in Maryland|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/md-politics/how-a-defiant-chelsea-manning-could-upend-the-race-for-us-senate-in-maryland/2018/01/16/3e77685c-fabf-11e7-a46b-a3614530bd87_story.html|accessdate=January 24, 2018|work=Washington Post|date=January 17, 2018|archive-date=2020-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215025637/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/md-politics/how-a-defiant-chelsea-manning-could-upend-the-race-for-us-senate-in-maryland/2018/01/16/3e77685c-fabf-11e7-a46b-a3614530bd87_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年8月，他宣布參選[[2020年美國總統選舉|2020年美國總統選舉]]<ref name=president>{{cite news |last=Chason |first=Rachel |date=28 August 2019 |title=Jerome Segal, of Maryland socialist Bread and Roses party, to run for president |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/md-politics/jerome-segal-of-maryland-socialist-bread-and-roses-party-to-run-for-president/2019/08/28/26a02ce8-c8f7-11e9-a4f3-c081a126de70_story.html?arc404=true |work=Washington Post |location=Washington DC |access-date=28 August 2019 |archive-date=2020-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201011013440/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/md-politics/jerome-segal-of-maryland-socialist-bread-and-roses-party-to-run-for-president/2019/08/28/26a02ce8-c8f7-11e9-a4f3-c081a126de70_story.html?arc404=true |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

